    "IdentifyThe process of developing an organizational understanding to manage cybersecurity risk concerning systems, assets, data, and capabilities is referred to the Identify function in the context of the NIST framework [15].",
    "Identifying potential risks is a crucial phase in risk management, and LLMs aim to fulfill a transformational role in forming risk management in businesses.",
    "Johnson [41] presents invaluable insights for policymakers on the applicability of LLMs to risk management.",
    "According to the author, LLMs go through business headlines, social media posts, economic indicators, legal documentation, and other key sources, emphasizing risk elements to deliver more accurate and predictive risk assessments that a human analyst might overlook.",
    "Lima et al. [17] develop a risk matrix from application reviews using LLMs."
